"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        KeyWrappingSpecification structs with different encoding options.
        """
a = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(encoding_option=enums.EncodingOption.
    NO_ENCODING)
b = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(encoding_option=enums.EncodingOption.
    TTLV_ENCODING)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
